{
  "stem": "4289.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Though, I remember in the beginning, when I went to school, the Jewish school, I used to stop by a church.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly, I stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I understood that I'm Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was going to a temple, which was not recommended by the Communist regime.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But since my stepmother was kind of a religious person, she made sure that I went to the shul on Rosh Hashanah, on Yom Kippur, and some Fridays.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did learn Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everybody was making fun of me, because my Yiddish had a Polish accent.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they were saying that, you better don't say anything.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Speak Polish, and we'll talk to you Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I did learn Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I even participated in some plays in school of Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I did realize I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that's who I am.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I-- at that age, a teenager, I learned a little bit from history, but not much.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My education came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I have to tell you before that, what happened.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did-- we were supposed to-- that was the rule, that we were supposed to study Hebrew half a day and then work a little bit and help out in the kibbutz, because we did not pay a penny.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I loved that life in the kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First day, they put me to press shirts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know even where to begin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But somebody sat there and showed me how to do it correctly.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The next day, they took me to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there I learned how to wash dishes, cook [INAUDIBLE], how to do things that I didn't know from my home.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we didn't have all those, you know, detergents that they have.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were quite behind.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
